import React from 'react';
import {
  Box,
  Typography,
  Container,
  Paper,
  Grid,
  Avatar,
  Button,
  Card,
  CardContent,
  List,
  ListItem,
  ListItemText,
  ListItemIcon
} from '@mui/material';
import {
  Person,
  Email,
  CalendarToday,
  LocalHospital,
  Restaurant
} from '@mui/icons-material';

const ProfilePage = () => {
  const userData = {
    name: localStorage.getItem('userName') || '–ò–≤–∞–Ω –ò–≤–∞–Ω–æ–≤',
    email: localStorage.getItem('userEmail') || 'ivan@example.com',
    joinDate: '15 —è–Ω–≤–∞—Ä—è 2024',
    disease: '–°–∞—Ö–∞—Ä–Ω—ã–π –¥–∏–∞–±–µ—Ç 2 —Ç–∏–ø–∞',
    plansCreated: 3,
    favoriteRecipes: 12
  };

  const recentPlans = [
    { id: 1, name: '–î–∏–∞–±–µ—Ç–∏—á–µ—Å–∫–∏–π —Ä–∞—Ü–∏–æ–Ω –Ω–∞ –Ω–µ–¥–µ–ª—é', date: '2024-01-15' },
    { id: 2, name: '–ù–∏–∑–∫–æ—É–≥–ª–µ–≤–æ–¥–Ω–æ–µ –ø–∏—Ç–∞–Ω–∏–µ', date: '2024-01-10' },
    { id: 3, name: '–°–±–∞–ª–∞–Ω—Å–∏—Ä–æ–≤–∞–Ω–Ω–∞—è –¥–∏–µ—Ç–∞', date: '2024-01-05' }
  ];

  return (
    <Container maxWidth="lg" style={{ padding: '32px 0' }}>
      <Typography variant="h4" component="h1" gutterBottom style={{ fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
        üë§ –ü—Ä–æ—Ñ–∏–ª—å –ø–æ–ª—å–∑–æ–≤–∞—Ç–µ–ª—è
      </Typography>

      <Grid container spacing={4}>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
          <Paper style={{ padding: '24px', textAlign: 'center' }}>
            <Avatar
              style={{
                width: 100,
                height: 100,
                margin: '0 auto 16px auto',
                backgroundColor: '#2E8B57',
                fontSize: '2rem'
              }}
            >
              {userData.name.split(' ').map(n => n[0]).join('')}
            </Avatar>
            
            <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom style={{ fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
              {userData.name}
            </Typography>
            
            <List>
              <ListItem>
                <ListItemIcon>
                  <Email />
                </ListItemIcon>
                <ListItemText primary="Email" secondary={userData.email} />
              </ListItem>
              <ListItem>
                <ListItemIcon>
                  <CalendarToday />
                </ListItemIcon>
                <ListItemText primary="–î–∞—Ç–∞ —Ä–µ–≥–∏—Å—Ç—Ä–∞—Ü–∏–∏" secondary={userData.joinDate} />
              </ListItem>
              <ListItem>
                <ListItemIcon>
                  <LocalHospital />
                </ListItemIcon>
                <ListItemText primary="–û—Å–Ω–æ–≤–Ω–æ–µ –∑–∞–±–æ–ª–µ–≤–∞–Ω–∏–µ" secondary={userData.disease} />
              </ListItem>
            </List>

            <Button variant="contained" fullWidth style={{ marginTop: '16px' }}>
              –†–µ–¥–∞–∫—Ç–∏—Ä–æ–≤–∞—Ç—å –ø—Ä–æ—Ñ–∏–ª—å
            </Button>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>

        <Grid item xs={12} md={8}>
          <Grid container spacing={3}>
            <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
              <Card>
                <CardContent style={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>
                  <Restaurant style={{ fontSize: 48, color: '#2E8B57', marginBottom: '8px' }} />
                  <Typography variant="h4" style={{ fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
                    {userData.plansCreated}
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                    –°–æ–∑–¥–∞–Ω–Ω—ã—Ö –ø–ª–∞–Ω–æ–≤
                  </Typography>
                </CardContent>
              </Card>
            </Grid>

            <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
              <Card>
                <CardContent style={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>
                  <Person style={{ fontSize: 48, color: '#3182CE', marginBottom: '8px' }} />
                  <Typography variant="h4" style={{ fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
                    {userData.favoriteRecipes}
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                    –õ—é–±–∏–º—ã—Ö —Ä–µ—Ü–µ–ø—Ç–æ–≤
                  </Typography>
                </CardContent>
              </Card>
            </Grid>

            <Grid item xs={12}>
              <Paper style={{ padding: '24px' }}>
                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom style={{ fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
                  üìã –ü–æ—Å–ª–µ–¥–Ω–∏–µ –ø–ª–∞–Ω—ã –ø–∏—Ç–∞–Ω–∏—è
                </Typography>
                <List>
                  {recentPlans.map((plan) => (
                    <ListItem key={plan.id} divider>
                      <ListItemText
                        primary={plan.name}
                        secondary={`–°–æ–∑–¥–∞–Ω: ${plan.date}`}
                      />
                      <Button variant="outlined" size="small">
                        –û—Ç–∫—Ä—ã—Ç—å
                      </Button>
                    </ListItem>
                  ))}
                </List>
              </Paper>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default ProfilePage;
